These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, green, amber, emerald
House: victorian, craftsman, wooden, ranch-style
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, funk, hip-hop, techno
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, chess, woodworking, drawing
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, skateboard, subway
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 2. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
 3. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
 4. the victorian house is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 9. the person driving the subway is the person who likes orange##1
10. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
11. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
13. the fan of techno is not to the right of the person who likes amber##8
14. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
15. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
16. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Color    | emerald | green     | amber     | orange |
| House        | craftsman  | victorian | wooden      | ranch-style      |
| Music-Genre         | techno  | funk    | hip-hop | r&b       |
| Hobby       | camping | chess   | woodworking      | drawing  |
| Transport   | bus      | airplane  | skateboard   | subway      |

