 8. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 9. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
10. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
11. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
12. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
13. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person eating corn##5
14. the person eating zucchini is the person playing monopoly##1
15. the person eating corn is not to the left of the person who likes azure##8
16. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the left of the person eating corn##8
17. the person eating cranberry is the person playing backgammon##1
