The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, classical, rock, r&b
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, september, february
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, snake, goldfish, hedgehog
 1. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the fan of rock##5
 2. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##8
 5. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the fan of classical##8
 7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 8. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the argentine is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
11. the argentine is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
13. the person who's birthday is in april is not the argentine##6
14. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8
15. the fan of r&b is between the person playing monopoly and the canadian##2
16. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Game          | billiard   | mah-jongg   | monopoly    | poker      |
| Music-Genre         | rock  | r&b | techno    | classical    |
